title: Episode 240: Post Traumatic Sex Disorder (Feat. G Herbo)
itunes:title: Episode 240: Post Traumatic Sex Disorder (Feat. G Herbo)
description:
Herbo opens up about his love for his girlfriend Taina, the traumas he’s faced during his childhood, and much more. Angela even has him translate scenarios from a male’s perspective, asking, “What does it mean when you cum too fast?” Enjoy!

*Disclaimer: This was filmed and recorded before the spread of COVID-19
